# HealthSentinel Root Gitignore

# --- Wildcard Matches (Recursive) ---
**/node_modules/
**/__pycache__/
**/venv/
**/.venv/
**/env/
**/.next/
**/.pytest_cache/

# --- Environment & Secrets ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Build Outputs ---
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/

# --- OS & IDE ---
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.log

# --- Docker ---
.docker/
